                    <description>In the macos x86_64 build with &amp;#39;--enable-ubsan&amp;#39; set, we run deterministically into this error :&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
/jdk/src/hotspot/share/prims/unsafe.cpp:162:38: runtime error: applying non-zero offset 4563897424 to null pointer&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;#0 0x10e37a724 in index_oop_from_field_offset_long(oop, long) unsafe.cpp:162&lt;br/&gt;
